{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/cp53o5/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/cp53o5","relativePath":"posts/cp53o5","frontmatter":{"title":"程序员宅家被愚弄","stackbit_url_path":"posts/cp53o5","date":"2022-04-03T01:59:37","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>前天愚人节，上海浦西正式开始封锁，被告知连扔垃圾都不许，只能放门口，由志愿者统一清理。这……，对不愿出门的我来说，简直就是福利呀！</p>\n<p>由于在家办公，决定折腾一番自己放在角落的 N 年前的台式机，扔掉过时的显式器键盘，换上公司发的在家办公套装，开机，发现完美运行，Windows 10 家庭版的系统，开屏界面还是很漂亮的。</p>\n<p>公司的新屏幕虽好，但是字体看上去不太舒服，想想自己这几年，在 Mac 电脑上使用程序员字体习惯了，回到 Windows 版本的默认字体，感觉就是怪怪的，于是动手安装字体。</p>\n<p>依次使用过 Fira Code、Victor Mono、JetbrainMonos。发现还是后者最舒服，于是就在 Windows 电脑上安装了 JetbrainMonos，效果立竿见影，看着极度舒适，非常棒。</p>\n<p>折腾完毕，开始工作，开始工作就得打开 StackOverflow，一打开 StackOverflow 就傻眼了：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/76435/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.91891891891892%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1648950098881 ef4a9ab1 b4e4 4bea be41 890fffcf82aa\"\n        title=\"1648950098881 ef4a9ab1 b4e4 4bea be41 890fffcf82aa\"\n        src=\"/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/fcda8/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/12f09/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png 148w,\n/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/e4a3f/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png 295w,\n/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/fcda8/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png 590w,\n/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/efc66/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png 885w,\n/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/c83ae/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png 1180w,\n/static/9a3c2796567c2f4f56111b5e04107d92/76435/1648950098881-ef4a9ab1-b4e4-4bea-be41-890fffcf82aa.png 1742w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>整个页面看得我头晕目眩。我对比了其他网站，还有其他地方的系统，发现都是好的，就只有 StackOverflow 的显示变坏了。</p>\n<p>JetbrainsMono 这么好，但怎么能偏偏在程序员必上网站上出问题呢？于是认真地向 JetbrainsMono 报告了这个问题。<a href=\"https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono/issues/536\">https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono/issues/536</a></p>\n<p>第二天，得到好心人回复，这不是 JetbrainsMono 的问题，这是 StackOverflow 的愚人节玩笑！原来我是做了一回愚人呀……</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/66632/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.21621621621621%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/fcda8/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/12f09/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png 148w,\n/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/e4a3f/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png 295w,\n/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/fcda8/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png 590w,\n/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/efc66/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png 885w,\n/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/c83ae/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png 1180w,\n/static/2fc3a837d11c33c5af3937bb6ba21f69/66632/1648950434719-a696803b-aefe-4aea-a5f3-38dda5ef871b.png 1504w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>第二天打开 StackOverflow，果然显示上恢复清晰状态了，但还有 Top Secret 等玩笑在……</p>\n<p>好吧，没想到，居然被自己天天上的网站给愚弄了一回。</p>\n<p><a name=iU3Xu></a></p>\n<h1>JetbrainsMono 安装</h1>\n<p>最后顺便说一下，在 Windows 上如果安装 JetbrainsMono 字体。</p>\n<p>powershell\nsudo choco install jetbrainsmono</p>\n<p>如果没有安装过 sudo，需要先使用管理员权限打开一个命令行：</p>\n<p>powershell\nchoco install sudo</p>\n<p>如果连 choco 都没有安装过，需要先使用管理员权限打开 Powershell，执行：</p>\n<p>powershell\nSet-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString(<a href=\"https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1\">https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1</a>))</p>\n<p><a name=ubt3R></a></p>\n<h1>安装后的好处</h1>\n<p>除了普通的代码展示更好之外，还有一些其他的好处，比如：在命令行里也能显示一些漂亮的字符了，而不再是乱码。（Windows 电脑的 cmd，如果不安装这种程序员字体，有些命令打印的 fancy 的字符，就会是一些乱码一样）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f3af67ffb5e5750b67353579b5cda037/6e6fb/1648950951268-308c50b9-7fa3-4ae8-adef-2d19c868cf80.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.513513513513516%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/f3af67ffb5e5750b67353579b5cda037/fcda8/1648950951268-308c50b9-7fa3-4ae8-adef-2d19c868cf80.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f3af67ffb5e5750b67353579b5cda037/12f09/1648950951268-308c50b9-7fa3-4ae8-adef-2d19c868cf80.png 148w,\n/static/f3af67ffb5e5750b67353579b5cda037/e4a3f/1648950951268-308c50b9-7fa3-4ae8-adef-2d19c868cf80.png 295w,\n/static/f3af67ffb5e5750b67353579b5cda037/fcda8/1648950951268-308c50b9-7fa3-4ae8-adef-2d19c868cf80.png 590w,\n/static/f3af67ffb5e5750b67353579b5cda037/6e6fb/1648950951268-308c50b9-7fa3-4ae8-adef-2d19c868cf80.png 618w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageed